    <item>
      <title>特朗普赞扬了两个月前被他称为“糟糕”的佐治亚州州长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/trump-praises-georgia-governor-kemp-he-called-bad-two-months-ago</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普公开赞扬了佐治亚州州长布莱恩·坎普。此前，这两位政客之间多年来一直存在激烈争论。特朗普曾将自己在 2020 年大选中的失败归咎于关键摇摆州的领导人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/trump-praises-georgia-governor-kemp-he-called-bad-two-months-ago</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 20:54:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
